---
import ContentLayout from '../layouts/ContentLayout.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<ContentLayout title="博客">
  <Section>
    <h2>Latest Posts</h2>
    <p>这里记录一些学习笔记和技术思考。</p>

    <article class="blog-item">
      <div class="blog-meta">
        <time datetime="2024-01-15">2024年1月15日</time>
      </div>
      <h3>如何构建高效的前端架构</h3>
      <p class="blog-desc">前端架构设计的最佳实践...</p>
      <a href="#" class="read-more">阅读更多 →</a>
    </article>

    <article class="blog-item">
      <div class="blog-meta">
        <time datetime="2024-01-10">2024年1月10日</time>
      </div>
      <h3>TypeScript 进阶指南</h3>
      <p class="blog-desc">TypeScript 高级类型系统的应用...</p>
      <a href="#" class="read-more">阅读更多 →</a>
    </article>

    <article class="blog-item">
      <div class="blog-meta">
        <time datetime="2024-01-05">2024年1月5日</time>
      </div>
      <h3>微服务架构实践</h3>
      <p class="blog-desc">大型应用中的微服务设计模式...</p>
      <a href="#" class="read-more">阅读更多 →</a>
    </article>
  </Section>
  <Footer />
</ContentLayout>

<style>
  .blog-item {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .blog-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .blog-meta {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .blog-item h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .blog-desc {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .read-more {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .read-more:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
